        "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/aai-rest-client-master-verify-java/17/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/aai-rest-client-master-verify-java/17",
