        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-12 17:29:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nInteresting.  Ok.  Good to know.  Originally when I tried to do the git review it failed because it said that I had to link in an issue-id.  I assumed it had to be part of the commit message.  Next time I'll add another line into the commit-msg for the issue-id.\n\nthx.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
